---
title: Dutch Pork Filet with Orange-Dijon Sauce with Mashed Potatoes, Roasted Carrots & Almonds
description: We’re going global with this gold medal winner from HF in the Netherlands! You’ll whip up a delectable pan sauce with fresh orange juice, tangy Dijon mustard, and a touch of butter and brown sugar, then spoon it over juicy pork filets. Sweet roasted carrots and buttery mashed potatoes round it all out, along with a sprinkle of nutty almonds for crunchy contrast.
